gy-global-posts-profit-of-rs-414-crore-in-fy24-124060600641_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22It%20said%20with%20the%20company%20signing%202.2%20GW%20of%20power%20purchase%20agreements%20(PPAs)%20towards%20the%20end%20of%20the%20financial%20year%2C%20its%20portfolio%20has%20grown%20to%2015.6%20GW%2C%20as%20of%20May%202024%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fnasdaq-listed-renew-energy-global-posts-profit-of-rs-414-crore-in-fy24-124060600641_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fnasdaq-listed-renew-energy-global-posts-profit-of-rs-414-crore-in-fy24-124060600641_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fnasdaq-listed-renew-energy-global-posts-profit-of-rs-414-crore-in-fy24-124060600641_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20United%20Arab%20Emirates%20pursued%20nearly%20%24100%20billion%20worth%20of%20oil%20and%20gas%20deals%20the%20same%20year%20it%20led%20the%20global%20climate%20summit%2C%20analysis%20finds%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222121%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20yellow%20offshore%20gas%20platform%20burns%20methane%2C%20a%20potent%20greenhouse%20gas%20causing%20the%20climate%20crisis.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F656b251458e7c0c29a290244%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221414%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAn%20offshore%20gas%20platform%20burns%20methane%2C%20a%20potent%20greenhouse%20gas%20that%20is%20causing%20the%20climate%20crisis.%3Cp%3EGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EUAE's%20state-owned%20oil%20company%20brokered%20deals%20to%20boost%20fossil%20fuels%20at%20home%20and%20overseas%20in%202023.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20deals%20included%20supplying%20gas%20to%20China%20and%20expanding%20into%C2%A0%20Egypt%20and%20Azerbaijan.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EUAE%20led%20the%202023%20global%20climate%20summit%20that%20called%20for%20a%20transition%20away%20from%20fossil%20fuels.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20year%2C%20while%20the%20United%20Arab%20Emirates%20oversaw%20a%20historic%20agreement%20to%20fight%20the%20climate%20crisis%2C%20it%20was%20brokering%20deals%20for%20oil%20and%20gas%20that%20could%20bring%20the%20country%20tens%20of%20billions%20of%20dollars%20and%20boost%20fossil-fuel%20production%20globally.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.globalwitness.org%2Fen%2Fcampaigns%2Ffossil-gas%2Fi-hope-the-younger-generations-can-forgive-us-state-oil-company-pushed-100-billion-of-deals-in-uaes-year-as-cop28-host%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eanalysis%20by%20the%20climate%20watchdog%20Global%20Witness%3C%2Fa%3E%20found%20that%20the%20UAE's%20state-owned%20oil%20company%2C%20known%20as%20ADNOC%2C%20closed%20more%20than%20a%20dozen%20deals%20to%20expand%20its%20oil%20and%20gas%20footprint%20at%20home%20and%20overseas.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmong%20the%20transactions%20were%20ADNOC's%20first%20contract%20to%20supply%20gas%20to%20China%3B%20a%20joint%20venture%20with%20the%20oil%20giant%20BP%20in%20Egypt%3B%20and%20a%20stake%20in%20Azerbaijan's%20gas%20field%20in%20the%20Caspian%20Sea.%20ADNOC%20also%20bought%20a%20Dutch%20fertilizer%20company%20and%20acquired%20a%20stake%20in%20an%20Austrian%20plastics%20maker%2C%20both%20of%20which%20rely%20on%20fossil%20fuels%20for%20their%20products.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20November%2C%20during%20the%20UN%20climate%20summit%20in%20Dubai%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcop28-host-uae-broker-secret-oil-deals-climate-summit-bbc-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20BBC%20and%20the%20Center%20for%20Climate%20Reporting%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported%20that%20UAE%20planning%20documents%20showed%20that%20oil%2C%20gas%2C%20petrochemical%2C%20and%20renewable-energy%20projects%20were%20among%20the%20talking%20points%20for%20meetings%20with%20countries%20in%20the%20lead-up%20to%20the%20climate%20summit%2C%20COP28.%20The%20summit%20was%20led%20by%20ADNOC's%20chief%20executive%2C%20Sultan%20Al%20Jaber.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGlobal%20Witness%20found%20that%20ADNOC%20either%20pursued%20or%20closed%20fossil-fuel%20deals%20with%20firms%20in%2011%20of%20the%2016%20countries%20targeted%20in%20the%20UAE%20planning%20documents.%20These%20included%20deals%20to%20sell%20liquefied%20natural%20gas%20to%20Chinese-owned%20firms%20and%20to%20expand%20oil%20and%20gas%20businesses%20in%20Egypt%20and%20Azerbaijan%20%E2%80%94%20two%20countries%20that%20open%20up%20the%20UAE's%20access%20to%20Europe%20as%20it%20seeks%20non-Russian%20gas.%20Global%20Witness%20estimated%20that%20the%20overall%20value%20of%20the%20deals%20it%20analyzed%20was%20nearly%20%24100%20billion%2C%20though%20some%20haven't%20been%20finalized.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMake%20no%20mistake%2C%20COP28%20was%20hijacked%20by%20the%20interests%20of%20the%20fossil%20fuel%20industry%2C%20who%20weren't%20content%20simply%20to%20block%20or%20stall%20genuine%20climate%20policy%20but%20used%20the%20opportunity%20to%20pursue%20more%20climate-wrecking%20oil%20and%20gas%20deals%2C%26quot%3B%20Patrick%20Galey%2C%20a%20senior%20investigator%20at%20Global%20Witness%2C%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EADNOC%20did%20not%20return%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20from%20Business%20Insider%2C%20but%20Global%20Witness%20presented%20its%20findings%20to%20the%20oil%20giant.%20A%20spokesperson%20told%20Global%20Witness%20that%20the%20allegation%20that%20ADNOC%20used%20COP28%20to%20pursue%20business%20deals%20was%20%26quot%3Bcompletely%20baseless%20and%20false.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20spokesperson%20argued%20that%20COP28%20%26quot%3Bdelivered%20the%20biggest%20climate%20breakthroughs%26quot%3B%20since%20the%20Paris%20Agreement%20in%202015%2C%20when%20world%20leaders%20agreed%20to%20try%20to%20limit%20global%20warming%20to%201.5%20degrees%20Celsius%20above%20preindustrial%20levels.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ab608433-ab72-4ca8-86e5-40fa507c2070%5C%22%3EA%20historic%20deal%20in%20Dubai%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EA%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ipcc.ch%2Freport%2Fsixth-assessment-report-cycle%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epanel%20of%20hundreds%20of%20climate%20scientists%3C%2Fa%3E%20convened%20by%20the%20UN%20has%20said%20that%20temperature%20threshold%20is%20likely%20to%20be%20crossed%20within%20the%20next%20decade%2C%20pushing%20the%20planet%20toward%20a%20catastrophe%2C%20unless%20countries%20rapidly%20stop%20burning%20fossil%20fuels.%20They've%20said%20emissions%20from%20existing%20oil%2C%20gas%2C%20and%20coal%20infrastructure%20are%20on%20track%20to%20exceed%20the%20Paris%20Agreement%20goal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20far%2C%20the%20planet%20has%20warmed%20by%20about%201.1%20degrees%20Celsius%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-climate-change-crisis-extreme-weather-is-costing-you-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edeadly%20heat%20waves%2C%20wildfires%2C%20flooding%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fglobal-food-crisis-higher-prices-shortages-civil-unrest-2022-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edrought-caused%20famine%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20on%20the%20rise.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20COP28%20in%20Dubai%2C%20countries%20for%20the%20first%20time%20called%20for%20a%20transition%20away%20from%20fossil%20fuels%20this%20decade%20and%20for%20the%20tripling%20of%20renewable%20energy%20by%202030.%20In%20a%20side%20agreement%20brokered%20by%20the%20UAE%2C%20oil%20and%20gas%20companies%20accounting%20for%2040%25%20of%20global%20production%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcop28-un-climate-conference-oil-and-gas-methane-emissions-satellites-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epromised%20to%20nearly%20eliminate%20their%20methane%20emissions%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%202030.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20Dubai%20deal%20left%20the%20door%20open%20to%20more%20fossil-fuel%20production%20by%20promoting%20technology%20such%20as%20carbon%20capture%2C%20which%20is%20still%20in%20the%20early%20stages%20of%20development.%20The%20deal%20also%20said%20%26quot%3Btransitional%20fuels%26quot%3B%20could%20play%20a%20role%20in%20reducing%20emissions%20%E2%80%94%20a%20nod%20to%20gas%2C%20which%20is%20less%20polluting%20than%20coal%20but%20a%20major%20emitter%20of%20methane.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fclimateactiontracker.org%2Fcountries%2Fuae%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EClimate%20scientists%20have%20found%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20while%20the%20UAE%20is%20investing%20in%20renewable%20energy%2C%20carbon%20capture%2C%20and%20other%20low-carbon%20technologies%2C%20that%20activity%20is%20dwarfed%20by%20the%20country's%20fossil-fuel%20expansion.%20The%20UAE%2C%20the%20seventh-largest%20oil%20producer%2C%20is%20investing%20%24150%20billion%20to%20boost%20its%20own%20oil%20and%20gas%20production%20through%202027.%20Global%20Witness'%20investigation%20also%20sheds%20light%20on%20how%20the%20country%20is%20securing%20new%20markets%20overseas.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGaley%20said%20he%20was%20concerned%20that%20another%20petrostate%2C%20Azerbaijan%2C%20which%20is%20hosting%20this%20year's%20UN%20climate%20summit%2C%20could%20follow%20the%20UAE's%20lead.%20COP29%20is%20set%20to%20be%20led%20by%20Azerbaijan's%20ecology%20minister%2C%20Mukhtar%20Babayev%2C%20who%20spent%20nearly%20two%20decades%20in%20senior%20positions%20at%20the%20country's%20state-owned%20energy%20company%20until%20leaving%20in%202018.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAzerbaijan%20is%20an%20emerging%20economy%20that%20relies%20on%20oil%20and%20gas%20for%20nearly%20half%20of%20its%20GDP%20and%20more%20than%2092%25%20of%20its%20export%20revenue.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECOP29%20organizers%20didn't%20return%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20from%20BI.%20They%20told%20Global%20Witness%20that%20they%20%26quot%3Breject%20in%20the%20strongest%20terms%20the%20suggestion%20that%20Azerbaijan%20has%20a%20hidden%20agenda%26quot%3B%20in%20hosting%20the%20climate%20summit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fuae-strikes-oil-and-gas-deals-during-historic-climate-summit-2024-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717671661000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6660ceaad0b8e1c832cc535d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fuae-strikes-oil-and-gas-deals-during-historic-climate-summit-2024-6%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20UAE%20closed%20more%20than%20a%20dozen%20deals%20to%20expand%20its%20oil%20and%20gas%20footprint%20at%20home%20and%20overseas%2C%20an%20analysis%20by%20Global%20Witness%20found.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22cboudreau%40insider.com%20(Catherine%20Boudreau)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fuae-strikes-oil-and-gas-deals-during-historic-climate-summit-2024-6%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Monsoon%20reaches%20Maharashtra%2C%20likely%20to%20hit%20Mumbai%20by%20June%2010%3A%20IMD%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717671631000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2024-05%2F30%2Fthumb%2Ffeaturecrop%2F400X400%2F1717045289-7316.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Findia-news%2Fmonsoon-reaches-maharashtra-likely-to-hit-mumbai-by-june-10-imd-124060600620_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Several%20parts%20of%20Maharashtra%20have%20been%20witnessing%20severe%20water%20shortage%2C%20with%20high%20temperatures%20exacerbating%20the%20situation%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Findia-news%2Fmons