untries%20will%20have%20to%20create%20buffers%20to%20navigate%20this%20situation%20should%20headwinds%20materialise.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20domestic%20scenario%20shows%20healthy%20macro-markers%20adding%20to%20India's%20resilience%2C%20with%20fiscal%20consolidation%2C%20continuing%20disinflation%20and%20beefed-up%20corporate%20and%20bank%20balance%20sheets%20conspicuous.%20Mid-%20and%20large%20corporate%20balance%20sheets%20look%20particularly%20good%20after%20protracted%20de-leveraging.%3Cbr%3E%5CnAt%20banks%2C%20non-performing%20loans%20are%20at%20decadal%20lows.%20External%20macros%20are%20comfortable%20as%20well%2C%20marked%20by%20a%20narrow%20current%20account%20deficit%2C%20low%20short-term%20debt%20and%20ample%20forex%20reserves.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESumming%20up%20the%20push-pull%20parameters%20-%20especially%20the%20transmission%20of%20high%20interest%20rates%20and%20a%20likely%20decline%20in%20fiscal%20spending%20owing%20to%20the%20government's%20consolidation%20mandate%20-%20we%20expect%20India's%20GDP%20growth%20to%20moderate%20to%206.8%25%20this%20fiscal.%20Even%20so%2C%20India%20will%20continue%20to%20be%20the%20fastest-growing%20large%20economy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20medium%20term%20-%20or%20till%20the%20end%20of%20the%20current%20decade%20-%20CRISIL's%20base%20case%20is%20a%20healthy%20average%20growth%20of%206.7%25%20annually.%20That%20will%20take%20India's%20GDP%20closer%20to%20the%20%247-trillion%20mark%20by%20fiscal%202031%2C%20from%20%243.6%20trillion.%20Per%20capita%20income%20will%20catapult%20to%20%244%2C600%20from%20%242%2C600%2C%20making%20India%20a%20middle-income%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20far%2C%20so%20good.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20what%20about%20those%20tricky%20undercurrents%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20will%20need%20to%20focus%20on%20five%20priorities%20to%20increase%20resilience%2C%20create%20upsides%20to%20growth%2C%20and%20make%20it%20inclusive%20and%20sustainable.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E1)%20Avoid%20The%20Complacency%20Trap%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia's%20rebound%20in%20the%20face%20of%20elevated%20global%20risks%20in%20the%20post-pandemic%20world%20was%20a%20result%20of%20good%20policy%20choices.%20This%20should%20not%20breed%20complacency%20in%20policymaking%20and%20reforms.%20If%20India%20wants%20to%20maintain%20its%20stature%20as%20the%20fastest-growing%20large%20economy%20and%20grow%20even%20faster%2C%20it%20cannot%20take%20its%20foot%20off%20the%20reforms%20pedal.%20Reforms%20pay%20off%20with%20a%20lag.%20The%201991%20reforms%20boosted%20economic%20potential%2C%20but%20high%20growth%20materialised%20much%20later.%20Similarly%2C%20the%20seminal%20Goods%20and%20Services%20Tax%20(GST)%20was%20launched%20in%202017%2C%20but%20we%20are%20seeing%20material%20benefits%20only%20now.%20Over%20the%20next%20few%20years%2C%20the%20economy%20will%20gain%20from%20the%20ongoing%20infrastructure%20buildout%20and%20digitalisation%2C%20which%20are%20improving%20logistics%20and%20efficiencies.%20However%2C%20to%20sustain%20long-term%20growth%2C%20reforms%20must%20continue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E2)%20Roll%20Out%20Next%20Level%20Of%20Reforms%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20streamlining%20the%20GST%20and%20the%20Insolvency%20and%20Bankruptcy%20Code%2C%20the%20government%20needs%20to%20kick%20off%20the%20next%20level%20of%20reforms%20in%20land%2C%20labour%20and%20agriculture.%20Since%20they%20fall%20under%20the%20concurrent%20list%2C%20both%20the%20Central%20and%20state%20governments%20must%20move%20in%20tandem%2C%20which%20requires%20deft%20consensus-building.%20Moreover%2C%20these%20need%20to%20be%20implemented%20at%20the%20state%20level.%20The%20government%20made%20an%20attempt%20to%20simplify%20the%20complex%20labour%20laws%20by%20merging%20them%20into%20four%20codes%20a%20few%20years%20ago%2C%20but%20this%20is%20yet%20to%20be%20implemented.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E3)%20Strengthen%20Private%20Investment%20Cycle%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20post-pandemic%20recovery%20has%20largely%20been%20led%20by%20household%20investments%20and%20government%20spending%20on%20infrastructure.%20Consequently%2C%20investments%20have%20outpaced%20the%20economic%20growth%20rate%20and%20there%20is%20a%20significant%20rise%20in%20their%20share%20of%20GDP.%20The%20private%20sector%20has%20not%20been%20a%20major%20player%20in%20this%20investment%20revival%20despite%20competitive%20corporate%20tax%20rates%2C%20improved%20logistics%2C%20growing%20digitalisation%20and%20the%20Production%20Linked%20Incentive%20(PLI)scheme.%20More%20efforts%20to%20improve%20the%20ease%20of%20doing%20business%20and%20encourage%20large-scale%20private%20sector%20investments%20are%20crucial.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E4)%20Emphasise%20Sustainable%20Growth%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20is%20among%20the%20countries%20most%20vulnerable%20to%20climate%20change.%20Last%20year%20was%20the%20hottest%20on%20record%20globally.%20For%20India%2C%20it%20was%20the%20second-hottest%2C%20while%20August%20the%20driest%20month%20in%20123%20years.%20Heatwaves%2C%20changing%20rainfall%20patterns%20and%20physical%20damage%20from%20climate%20events%20will%20only%20intensify%20going%20ahead.%20Therefore%2C%20urgent%20efforts%20are%20needed%20to%20adapt%20to%20and%20minimise%20risks.%20To%20be%20sure%2C%20better%20preparedness%2C%20including%20setting%20up%20of%20early%20warning%20systems%20over%20recent%20years%2C%20has%20helped.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMitigation%20strategies%20must%20include%20developing%20climate-resistant%20crops%2C%20more%20early%20warning%20systems%20and%20smart%20infrastructure%2C%20and%20industry%20planning.%20Agriculture%20needs%20to%20be%20made%20resilient.%20Not%20only%20is%20it%20the%20most%20vulnerable%20to%20climate%20change%2C%20but%20a%20large%20part%20of%20the%20population%20depends%20on%20it.%20Elevated%20food%20inflation%20-%20which%20has%20been%20thwarting%20changes%20in%20the%20interest%20rate%20cycle%20-%20is%20related%20to%20weather%20vagaries.%20From%20a%20long-term%20perspective%2C%20India%20needs%20to%20decarbonise%20to%20be%20on%20the%20path%20to%20net-zero%20by%202070.%20And%20it%20has%20to%20balance%20that%20with%20the%20objective%20of%20ensuring%20energy%20security%20and%20its%20affordability%2C%20both%20of%20which%20are%20vital%20for%20growth%20and%20development.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E5)%20Create%20Jobs%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEmployment%20generation%20is%20a%20critical%20focus%20area.%20India%20has%20a%20predominantly%20young%20population%20and%20will%20contribute%20over%2020%25%20of%20the%20incremental%20global%20workforce%20over%20the%20next%20decade.%20In%20manufacturing%2C%20labour-intensive%20segments%20such%20as%20textiles%2C%20gems%20and%20jewellery%2C%20food%20processing%2C%20and%20leather%20and%20leather%20products%20need%20to%20be%20promoted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOf%20late%2C%20exports%20in%20these%20labour-intensive%20sectors%20have%20not%20done%20well%20and%20their%20share%20in%20total%20exports%20has%20consistently%20declined.%20Focusing%20on%20relatively%20labour-intensive%20services%2C%20such%20as%20healthcare%2C%20education%20and%20hospitality%2C%20will%20augment%20job%20creation.%20Public%20investment%20in%20healthcare%20and%20education%20will%20not%20only%20create%20jobs%20but%20also%20raise%20growth%20potential%20by%20making%20the%20workforce%20skilled%2C%20educated%20and%20healthy.%20This%20will%20allow%20a%20larger%20part%20of%20the%20workforce%20to%20participate%20in%20the%20growth%20process%20and%20reduce%20income%20inequality.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20this%20will%20set%20the%20scene%20for%20high%20and%20sustainable%20long-term%20growth%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Dharmakirti%20Joshi%20is%20Chief%20Economist%2C%20CRISIL%20Ltd)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717670880000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ndtvimg.com%2Fi%2F2016-06%2Fconstruction-infrastructure-real-estate_650x400_61465278345.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fact-3-take-one-five-economic-planks-the-new-government-must-focus-on-5831231%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Scan%20the%20landscape%2C%20and%20we%20foresee%20the%20global%20economy%20resilient%20in%202024.%20But%20a%20multitude%20of%20factors%20-%20geopolitical%20uncertainties%2C%20debt%20piles%2C%20tariff%20friction%20and%20climatic%20disruptions%20-%20seethe%20underneath.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fact-3-take-one-five-economic-planks-the-new-government-must-focus-on-5831231%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Obscene%20videos%20case%3A%20Prajwal's%20SIT%20custody%20extended%20till%20June%2010%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717670844000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-110767236%2Cimgsize-2386742.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fobscene-videos-case-prajwal-revannas-sit-custody-extended-till-june-10%2Farticleshow%2F110767185.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Bengaluru%20court%20sent%20Hassan%20MP%20Prajwal%20Revanna%20to%20SIT%20custody%20till%20June%2010%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20obscene%20videos%20case.%20Prajwal%20Revanna%2C%20accused%20of%20sexually%20assaulting%20three%20women%2C%20was%20swiftly%20arrested%20upon%20landing%20at%20Kempegowda%20International%20Airport.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20NEWS%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Jahnvi%20Kapoor%20once%20shoplifted%20candies%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717670835000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto