sofi-checking-savings-review%5C%22%3ESoFi%20Checking%20and%20Savings%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEarn%20up%20to%20%24300%20with%20qualifying%20direct%20deposit%20for%20eligible%20customers%20(offer%20expires%2012%2F31%2F24).%20Earn%20up%20to%204.60%25%20APY%20on%20savings%20balances%20(including%20Vaults)%20with%20direct%20deposit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ESee%20more%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fbest-bank-account-bonuses%5C%22%3Ebank%20account%20bonuses%20%3Cstrong%3E%C2%BB%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EAbout%20High-Yield%20Accounts%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EHigh-yield%20savings%20accounts%20aren't%20the%20only%20accounts%20paying%20favorable%20rates%20right%20now.%20You'll%20typically%20see%20the%20highest%20rates%20at%20online%20or%20lower-profile%20institutions%20rather%20than%20national%20brands%20with%20a%20significant%20brick-and-mortar%20presence.%20This%20is%20normal%3B%20online%20banks%20have%20lower%20overhead%20costs%20and%20are%20willing%20to%20pay%20high%20rates%20to%20attract%20new%20customers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EHigh-Yield%20Savings%20Accounts%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20best%20high-yield%20savings%20accounts%20provide%20the%20security%20of%20a%20savings%20account%20with%20the%20added%20bonus%20of%20a%20high%20APY.%20Savings%20accounts%20are%20held%20at%20a%20bank%20or%20credit%20union%20%E2%80%94%20not%20invested%20through%20a%20brokerage%20account%20%E2%80%94%20and%20are%20best%20for%20saving%20cash%20in%20pursuit%20of%20shorter-term%20goals%2C%20like%20a%20vacation%20or%20big%20purchase.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EHigh-Yield%20Checking%20Accounts%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20best%20high-yield%20checking%20accounts%20tend%20to%20pay%20slightly%20lower%20rates%20than%20high-yield%20savings%2C%20but%20even%20they%20are%20strong%20in%20today's%20rate%20environment.%20A%20checking%20account%20is%20like%20a%20hub%20for%20your%20money%3A%20If%20your%20paycheck%20is%20direct%20deposited%2C%20it's%20typically%20