2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22039eadac-102d-41b4-9c51-8cb79b4de600%5C%22%3E'The%20dangers%20are%20enough%20now'%20to%20put%20regulations%20in%20place%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20consequences%20of%20no%20comprehensive%20AI%20regulation%20soon%2C%20Bartholomew%20warned%2C%20include%20misinformation%20infecting%20elections%2C%20the%20spread%20of%20deepfakes%2C%20and%20people%20being%20defrauded%20by%20scammers%20using%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-voices-of-politicians-and-influencers-are-taking-over-tiktok-2023-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAI%20to%20simulate%20the%20voices%20of%20others%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20would%20be%20dangerous%20to%20say%20we%20know%20now%20in%202024%20exactly%20how%20to%20handle%20AI%2C%26quot%3B%20Bartholomew%20said%2C%20noting%20that%20too%20many%20regulations%20too%20soon%20could%20stifle%20%26quot%3Ba%20promising%20new%20technology%20like%20AI.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20he%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BMy%20personal%20opinion%20is%20that%20the%20dangers%20are%20enough%20now%20that%20we%20need%20to%20come%20in%20and%20at%20least%20have%20some%20specific%20regulations%20to%20deal%20with%20things%20that%20I%20think%20we're%20already%20realizing%20are%20real%20problems.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20not%20like%20AI%20will%20shrivel%20up%20and%20die%20if%20we%20put%20real%20teeth%20into%20laws%20saying%20you%20can't%20use%20AI%20for%20political%20deepfakes%2C%26quot%3B%20Bartholomew%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUS%20intellectual%20property%20laws%20related%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-copyright-office-proposed-changes-copyright-law-ai-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecopyright%20infringement%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20state-level%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-ai-will-change-music-entertainment-lawyers-2023-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epublicity%20rights%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20among%20the%20main%