ulation%20decline%20a%20greater%20threat%20than%20climate%20change%2C%20tweeted%20his%20support%20for%20the%20app.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20February%2C%20Japan's%20government%20said%20%26quot%3Bunprecedented%20steps%26quot%3B%20must%20be%20taken%20to%20tackle%20the%20country's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Feconomy-outlook-japan-aging-population-inflation-eurizon-recession-disinflation-markets-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erecord-low%20birth%20rates%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETokyo's%20government%20got%20the%20message.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20city%20has%20invested%20%241.28%20million%20in%20a%20dating%20app%20for%20its%20residents%2C%20due%20to%20be%20launched%20this%20summer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20app%2C%20run%20by%20a%20private%20contractor%2C%20has%20a%20rigorous%20registration%20process%20to%20ensure%20users%20are%20committed%20to%20marriage%20as%20an%20end%20goal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.asahi.com%2Fajw%2Farticles%2F15292637%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJapanese%20national%20newspaper%20The%20Asahi%20Shimbun%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20app%20requests%20not%20just%20a%20photo%20ID%20but%20also%20an%20income%20certificate%20and%20an%20official%20document%20confirming%20your%20relationship%20status.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20outlet%20said%20that%20there%20are%2015%20categories%20of%20personal%20data%20to%20fill%20out%20on%20the%20app%2C%20including%20height%2C%20education%2C%20and%20occupation%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0all%20of%20which%20will%20be%20visible%20to%20potential%20matches.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20that%2C%20users%20attend%20a%20mandatory%20interview%20with%20the%20app's%20operators%20before%20signing%20a%20pledge%20promising%20that%20they%20are%20looking%20for%20a%20marriage%20partner%20and%20not%20just%20a%20casual%20relationship.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20there%20are%20many%20individuals%20interested%20in%20marriage%20but%20unable%20to%20find%20a%20partner%2C%2