20contend%20with%20allies%20who%20will%20demand%20their%20pound%20of%20flesh.%20It's%20no%20secret%20that%20the%20two%20big%20NDA%20collaborators%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F2024-lok-sabha-election-result-what-chandrababu-naidu-nitish-kumar-want-for-backing-modi-3-0-5828872%5C%22%3ENitish%20Kumar-led%20Janata%20Dal%20(United)%20(JD-U)%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fopinion-post-verdict-2024-delhi-needs-to-learn-the-art-of-negotiating-5822761%5C%22%3EChandrababu%20Naidu-led%20Telugu%20Desam%20Party%20(TDP)%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20have%20a%20history%20of%20flitting%20in%20and%20out%20of%20the%20bloc.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThree%20Theories%20Flying%20Around%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20reaction%20of%20poll%20pundits%20has%20been%20to%20theorise%20that%20the%20BJP%20has%20lost%20its%20magic%20in%20the%20Hindi%20heartland%2C%20with%20the%20big%20slides%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20and%20Rajasthan%20being%20cited%20as%20proof.%20But%20then%2C%20most%20Delhi%20voters%20come%20from%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F2024-lok-sabha-election-result-tejashwi-yadav-chirag-paswan-akhilesh-yadav-3-sons-stepping-out-of-fathers-shadows-turn-heartland-gamechangers-5822014%5C%22%3Esame%20Hindi%20heartland%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20the%20BJP%20has%20won%20all%20seven%20seats%20here.%20It%20also%20won%20all%2029%20seats%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20and%20has%20almost%20swept%20Chhattisgarh%20and%20Jharkhand%20-%20in%20spite%20of%20the%20sympathy%20vote%20for%20Hemant%20Soren.%20Himachal%20Pradesh%20and%20Uttarakhand%20are%20also%20part%20of%20this%20landslide.%20Clearly%20then%2C%20the%20'lost%20Hindi%20heartland'%20theory%20is%20a%20bit%20far-fetched.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20second%20theory%20relates%20to%20voters'%20anger%20over%20unemployment%20and%20inflation.%20Serious%20concerns%20were%20expressed%20about%20these%20issues%20both%20before%20and%20during%20the%20elections.%20But%20if%20they%20did%20so%20decisively%20influence%20voting%20intent%2C%20how%20did%20the%20BJP%20do%20so%20well%20in%20the%20states%20mentioned%20above%3F%20Not%20just%20that%2C%20inflation%20and%20unemployment%20seem%20to%20have%20had%20little%20effect%20on%20voters%20in%20Odisha%20and%20Telangana.%20It's%20also%20not%20clear%20how%20and%20why%20the%20BJP%20finally%20succeeded%20in%20penetrating%20south%20India%20by%20gaining%20considerable%20vote%20shares%20as%20well%20as%20a%20few%20seats.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Flok-sabha-election-result-how-everyone-failed-to-read-the-tea-leaves-against-bjp-in-uttar-pradesh-5818762%5C%22%3ERead%20%7C%C2%A0How%20Almost%20Everyone%20Missed%20The%20All-Too-Visible%20Signs%20In%20Uttar%20Pradesh%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20third%20theory%20is%20that%20the%20Hindutva%20pitch%20has%20failed%20to%20deliver%20any%20significant%20gains%20to%20the%20BJP%20despite%20the%20grand%20inauguration%20of%20the%20Ram%20Temple%20in%20Ayodhya%20in%20January%20this%20year.%20On%20the%20face%20of%20it%2C%20this%20theory%20may%20sound%20plausible.%20But%20then%20again%2C%20it'd%20be%20erroneous%20to%20believe%20that%20Hindutva%20works%20in%20a%20few%20states%20and%20doesn't%20in%20a%20few%20others.%20So%20one%20can%20safely%20dispense%20with%20this%20theory%2C%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20Widely%20Scattered%20Verdict%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20thing%2C%20however%2C%20remains%20common%20across%20most%20defeated%20BJP%20candidates%3A%20the%20losing%20names%20were%20either%20hugely%20unpopular%20in%20their%20own%20areas%20or%20were%20'imports'%20from%20other%20parties%2C%20with%20whom%20their%20own%20party%20'%3Cem%3Ekaryakartas%3C%2Fem%3E'%20were%20not%20very%20happy.%20Even%20the%20'Vote%20for%20Modi'%20pitch%20could%20not%20induce%20them%20to%20look%20past%20their%20frustration.%20A%20second%20important%20problem%20was%20the%20'%3Cem%3Ejod%20tod%20ki%20rajneeti%3C%2Fem%3E'%20that%20played%20out%20in%20Maharashtra.%20For%20almost%2018%20months%2C%20the%20CVoter%20Mood%20Of%20The%20Nation%20(MOTN)%20survey%20had%20been%20flagging%20the%20discontent%20in%20Maharashtra%20over%20its%20patchwork%20government.%20The%20actual%20results%20now%20prove%20this.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20quick%20look%20at%20the%20numbers%20will%20showcase%20how%20fractured%20the%20verdict%20has%20been.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ELet's%20start%20with%20Uttar%20Pradesh.%20From%2062%20in%202019%2C%20the%20BJP%20tally%20has%20come%20down%20to%2036.%20That's%20a%20shocking%20drop.%20But%20not%20a%20whiff%20of%20this%20was%20caught%20in%20nearby%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20where%20the%20BJP%20bagged%20all%2029%20seats.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIn%20Delhi%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20managed%20to%20sweep%20all%20seven%20seats%2C%20but%20in%20nearby%20Haryana%2C%20it%20could%20barely%20manage%20to%20hold%20on%20to%20five.%20Gujarat%20has%20more%20or%20less%20returned%20a%20sweeping%20victory.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIn%20Karnataka%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20lost%20eight%20seats%2C%20and%20in%20Maharashtra%2C%20it%20has%20been%20reduced%20to%20just%20nine%20seats%20against%20its%202019%20tally%20of%2023.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIn%20West%20Bengal%2C%20the%20party%20lost%20at%20least%20six%20seats%20against%20its%20victory%20in%2018%20in%20the%20previous%20general%20election.%20On%20the%20contrary%2C%20in%20nearby%20Odisha%2C%20the%20BJP%20tally%20has%20shot%20up%20from%20eight%20to%2019.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EQuite%20a%20confusing%20picture%2C%20isn't%20it%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJust%20as%20many%20said%20during%20the%20election%20campaign%2C%20there%20is%20no%20single%20national%20narrative.%20The%20final%20verdict%20demonstrates%20that%20the%20choices%20of%20the%20same%20sets%20of%20voters%20%C2%A0-%20education%2C%20gender%2C%20ethnic%20identity%2C%20etc%2C%20being%20common%20parameters%20-%20were%20not%20influenced%20by%20any%20'national'%20narrative.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20brings%20us%20to%20the%20final%20question%3A%20how%20did%20all%20the%20exit%20polls%20get%20it%20so%20wrong%3F%20Even%20most%20conservative%20estimates%20had%20said%20that%20the%20NDA%20will%20comfortably%20touch%20350%20seats.%20The%20actual%20tally%20turned%20out%20to%20be%20over%2050%20seats%20less%20than%20that.%20The%20answer%20to%20this%20query%20could%20have%20been%20easier%20to%20deduce%20if%20there%20was%20some%20degree%20of%20uniformity%20in%20the%20results%20across%20India.%20But%20there%20isn't.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20the%20verdict%20is%20so%20scattered%2C%20the%20authors%20have%20identified%20two%20reasons%20for%20the%20so-called%20%26quot%3Bdebacle%26quot%3B%20of%20the%20BJP.%20To%20be%20fair%2C%20any%20other%20party%20winning%20about%20244%20seats%20after%20two%20terms%20would%20have%20been%20applauded.%20But%20the%20great%20hype%20and%20expectations%20that%20the%20BJP%20generated%20around%20it%20have%20sort%20of%20backfired%2C%20painting%20even%20a%20clear%20NDA%20victory%20as%20some%20sort%20of%20defeat.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Farrogance-evms-and-uttar-pradesh-election-2024s-key-lessons-5824845%5C%22%3ERead%20%7C%20Arrogance%2C%20EVMs%20And%20Uttar%20Pradesh%3A%20Key%20Lessons%20From%20Election%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20co-author%20also%20travelled%20across%20India%20for%20three%20months%20in%20the%20run-up%20to%20the%20elections%20and%20found%20two%20things.%20One%20was%20that%20Modi%20remained%20very%20popular.%20And%20second%2C%20a%20majority%20of%20families%20were%20struggling%20to%20make%20ends%20meet%20and%20were%20not%20happy%20with%20their%20economic%20situation.%20Now%2C%20they%20did%20not%20say%20that%20this%20economic%20distress%20would%20translate%20into%20a%20vote%20against%20the%20BJP%2C%20particularly%20in%20places%20where%20the%20local%20candidate%20was%20unpopular.%20Our%20large%20CVoter%20team%20that%20fanned%20out%20across%20India%20also%20did%20not%20see%20any%20response%20that%20indicated%20a%20vote%20against%20the%20BJP.%20Yet%2C%20it%20is%20clear%20as%20day%20that%20ultimately%2C%20the%20silent%20voter%20remained%20silent%20and%20voted%20against%20the%20local%20BJP%20candidate.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20coming%20days%2C%20as%20more%20detailed%20constituency-wise%20analyses%20are%20done%2C%20the%20authors%20do%20not%20doubt%20that%20the%20defeated%20candidates%20would%20turn%20out%20to%20be%20those%20who%20had%20been%20unpopular%20with%20local%20voters.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20related%20addendum%20to%20all%20this%20is%20internal%20rift%20and%20sabotage.%20In%20most%20major%20parties%2C%20there%20are%20factions%20that%20jostle%20for%20space.%20Often%2C%20these%20rivalries%20are%20settled%20in%20the%20name%20of%20a%20bigger%20goal%3A%20making%20the%20party%20win.%20That%20did%20not%20happen%20in%20the%20BJP's%20case%20this%20time.%20In%20hindsight%2C%20it%20can%20now%20be%20argued%20that%20the%20party%20was%20hit%20badly%20by%20internal%20rifts%20and%20sabotage%2C%20and%20the%20impact%20is%20clearly%20visible%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20and%20Rajasthan.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP's%20task%20now%20is%20to%20draw%20substantive%20lessons%20from%20this%20verdict.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Yashwant%20Deshmukh%20is%20the%20Founder%20and%20Editor-in-Chief%20of%20CVoter%20Foundation%2C%20and%20Sutanu%20Guru%20is%20the%20Executive%20Director)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20views%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717665960000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Fimd1uado_image_640x480_01_June_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fhow-did-exit-polls-fail-to-capture-ground-reality-a-pollster