%201%2C87%2C251%20votes.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20recent%20interview%20with%20NDTV%2C%20Ms%20Choudhary%20discussed%20her%20remarkable%20achievement.%20Addressing%20the%20challenges%20of%20contesting%20in%20Bihar's%20deeply%20caste-driven%20society%2C%20Ms%20Choudhary%2C%20a%20part%20of%20the%20NDA%20coalition%2C%20said%20she%20had%20only%20focussed%20on%20development%20over%20divisive%20issues.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20I%20went%20to%20the%20constituency%2C%20I%20did%20not%20talk%20of%20caste%20or%20religion%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20stated.%20%26quot%3BI%20only%20talked%20about%20the%20development%20that%20has%20happened%20in%20Bihar%20in%20the%20last%20decade.%26quot%3B%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EElaborating%20on%20her%20approach%2C%20she%20stressed%20the%20importance%20of%20engaging%20with%20constituents%20on%20issues%20pertinent%20to%20their%20lives%20and%20presenting%20a%20clear%20vision%20for%20progress.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20talked%20about%20our%20vision%2C%20goals%2C%20and%20I%20especially%20tried%20to%20meet%20as%20many%20people%20as%20I%20could%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added%2C%20claiming%20that%20she%20often%20spent%2016-17%20hours%20a%20day%20on%20the%20field%2C%20discussing%20various%20plans%20and%20aspirations%20with%20the%20electorate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Chaudhary%2C%20whose%20father%20Ashok%20Choudhary%20is%20a%20senior%20leader%20in%20the%20ruling%20Janta%20Dal%20(United)%2C%20was%20next%20asked%20about%20her%20affiliation%20with%20the%20LJP%2C%20a%20smaller%20ally%20of%20the%20JD(U)%20and%20the%20BJP%20in%20Bihar.%20%26quot%3BI%20am%20young%2C%20I%20am%20a%20youth%2C%20and%20I%20think%20I%20connect%20with%20youth%20more%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20stated.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20was%20confident%20in%20the%20leadership%20of%20party%20president%20Chirag%20Paswan.%20She%20also%20spoke%20about%20the%20LJP's%20track%20record%20of%20consistent%20electoral%20wins%20despite%20recent%20changes%2C%20including%20the%20renaming%20of%20the%20party%20to%20Lok%20Janshakti%20Party%20(Ram%20Vilas)%20and%20its%20symbol%20change%20from%20a%20bungalow%20to%20a%20helicopter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDespite%20all%20these%20consequences%2C%20we%20have%20a%20100%25%20strike%20rate%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20proudly%20declared.%20%26quot%3BAll%20the%20candidates%20from%20our%20party%20have%20been%20winning.%20We%20have%20worked%20very%20hard%20and%20we%20have%20been%20successfully%20able%20to%20achieve%20this%20party%20as%20a%20key%20in%20Bihar%20politics%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%2025-year-old%20claimed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20if%20she%20had%20sought%20votes%20in%20the%20name%20of%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20Ms%20Choudhary%20acknowledged%20that%20%E2%80%9Cdefinitely%20there%20is%20a%20Modi%20factor%2C%20you%20can't%20deny%20it.%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%9CWe%20were%20also%20talking%20about%20Chief%20Minister%20Nitish%20Kumar%20ji%2C%20our%20party%20president%20Chirag%20Paswan%2C%20and%20respected%20late%20Ram%20Vilas%20Paswan%20ji%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20stated.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Choudhary%20has%20credited%20her%20win%20to%20a%20combination%20of%20factors%2C%20including%20leadership%20appeal%20and%20a%20well-defined%20%E2%80%9Croadmap%E2%80%9D%20tailored%20for%20her%20constituency.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20also%20talking%20about%20my%20own%20goals%2C%20my%20own%20vision%2C%20my%20own%20aspirations%20from%20the%20constituency%20that%20I%20have%20in%20mind%2C%E2%80%9D%20adding%20that%20%E2%80%9Call%20these%20factors%20are%20very%20crucial%20and%20all%20these%20factors%20came%20up%20together%20and%20that%20is%20how%20I%20could%20win%20with%20the%20second%20largest%20margin%20in%20the%20state.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717664700000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Fpngqe4n8_-shambhavi-choudhary_625x300_06_June_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnot-caste-factor-youngest-bihar-mp-sha