n%20to%20meet%20renewable%20energy%20target%3A%20Moody's%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717664592000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2023-12%2F06%2Fthumb%2Ffeaturecrop%2F400X400%2F1701843887-3248.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Ffinance%2Fnews%2Findia-to-spend-up-to-385-bn-to-meet-renewable-energy-target-moody-s-124060600452_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22India%2C%20a%20major%20greenhouse%20gas%20emitter%2C%20has%20said%20it%20aims%20to%20ramp%20up%20non-fossil%20fuel%20capacity%20set%20by%2050%20GW%20each%20year%20to%20help%20meet%20its%20500%20GW%20target.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Ffinance%2Fnews%2Findia-to-spend-up-to-385-bn-to-meet-renewable-energy-target-moody-s-124060600452_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Ffinance%2Fnews%2Findia-to-spend-up-to-385-bn-to-meet-renewable-energy-target-moody-s-124060600452_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Ffinance%2Fnews%2Findia-to-spend-up-to-385-bn-to-meet-renewable-energy-target-moody-s-124060600452_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Coalition-Era%20Impact%20On%20Modi%203.0%3A%20BJP's%20Key%20Ally%20Flags%20Agniveer%20Resentment%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20first%20sign%20that%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government's%20third%20term%20could%20be%20very%20different%20from%20the%20first%20two%2C%20a%20top%20Janata%20Dal%20United%20leader%20has%20said%20the%20party%20will%20seek%20a%20review%20of%20the%20Centre's%20Agnipath%20scheme%20for%20recruitment%20in%20the%20armed%20forces.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKC%20Tyagi%2C%20chief%20spokesperson%20of%20BJP%20ally%20JDU%20and%20among%20the%20closest%20aides%20of%20its%20chief%20Nitish%20Kumar%2C%20has%20said%20there%20is%20resentment%20against%20the%20scheme%20in%20several%20states.%20%26quot%3BThere%20is%20resentment%2C%20so%20we%20will%20seek%20a%20review%20of%20Agniveer.%20We%20are%20not%20opposing%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELaunched%20in%202022%2C%20Agnipath%20scheme%20provides%20for%20short-term%20induction%20of%20personnel%20into%20the%20armed%20forces%20with%20an%20aim%20to%20bring%20down%20the%20age%20profile%20of%20the%20three%20services.%20Those%20recruited%20under%20the%20scheme%20are%20called%20Agniveers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20the%20scheme%2C%20youngsters%20in%20the%2017.5%20years-21%20years%20age%20group%20are%20inducted%20for%20a%20four-year%20period.%20There%20is%20a%20provision%20to%20retain%2025%20per%20cent%20of%20these%20recruits%20for%2015%20more%20years.%20The%20remaining%20will%20be%20given%20a%20financial%20package%20as%20their%20service%20comes%20to%20an%20end.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnnouncement%20of%20the%20scheme%20had%20triggered%20violent%20protests%20in%20several%20parts%20of%20the%20country%20as%20youngsters%20preparing%20for%20an%20entry%20into%20armed%20forces%20opposed%20the%20short-term%20service%20plan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMain%20Opposition%20Congress%20opposed%20the%20new%20scheme%20and%20turned%20it%20into%20a%20key%20plank%20in%20their%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%20campaign.%20The%20party%20argued%20that%20the%20scheme%20will%20leave%20Agniveers%20unemployed%20at%20the%20age%20of%2025.%20It%20also%20said%20that%20it%20affect%20cohesion%20in%20the%20forces%20as%20short-term%20recruits%20serve%20alongside%20soldiers%20eligible%20for%20secure%20pensions%20and%20more%20generous%20allowances.%20The%20Congress%20questioned%20if%20Agniveer%20recruits%20will%20be%20motivated%20to%20risk%20their%20lives%20if%20they%20know%20that%20they%20are%20on%20a%20short-term%20service%20plan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Centre%20has%20argued%20that%20the%20Agnipath%20scheme%20is%20aimed%20at%20improving%20the%20battle%20preparedness%20in%20the%20armed%20forces%20and%20achieving%20a%20balance%20of%20youth%20and%20experience%20in%20ranks.%20They%20have%20also%20said%20that%20a%20good%20financial%20package%20to%20Agniveers%20at%20the%20end%20of%20their%20four-year%20service%20will%20give%20them%20a%20good%20head%20start%2C%20besides%20the%20unique%20experience%20of%20working%20in%20the%20forces%2C%20making%20their%20resume%20stand%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Tyagi%20also%20said%20a%20nationwide%20caste%20survey%20must%20be%20held%20and%20Bihar%20should%20get%20a%20special%20status.%20Significantly%2C%20a%20nationwide%20caste%20survey%20was%20one%20of%20the%20key%20poll%20planks%20of%20the%20INDIA%20Opposition%20bloc.%20Also%2C%20the%20Nitish%20Kumar%20government%20that%20was%20backed%20by%20the%20RJD%20and%20Congress%20had%20conducted%20a%20caste%20survey%20in%20the%20state%20before%20the%20JDU%20chief%20switched%20sides%20and%20joined%20hands%20with%20the%20NDA.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20JDU%20leader's%20remarks%20come%20at%20a%20time%20when%20Nitish%20Kumar%20and%20N%20Chandrababu%20Naidu%2C%20who%20have%20emerged%20kingmakers%20after%20BJP%20fell%20short%20of%20a%20majority%2C%20are%20bargaining%20hard%20for%20plum%20posts%20at%20the%20Centre.%20The%20JDU%2C%20sources%20said%2C%20may%20also%20insist%20on%20a%20Common%20Minimum%20Programme%20for%20the%20new%20NDA%20government.%20In%20the%20past%20two%20terms%20of%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%2C%20the%20BJP%20held%20absolute%20majority%20and%20was%20free%20to%20take%20its%20decisions.%20But%20the%20return%20of%20the%20coalition-era%20has%20changed%20things.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%2C%20results%20of%20which%20were%20out%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20the%20BJP%20won%20240%20seats%20--%2032%20short%20of%20the%20majority%20mark%20of%20272%20in%20Lok%20Sabha.%20TDP%20(16)%20and%20JDU%20(12)%20together%20hold%2028%20seats%20and%20along%20with%20BJP's%20other%20allies%2C%20the%20NDA%20tally%20will%20be%20past%20the%20magic%20figure.%20The%20INDIA%20Opposition%20bloc%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20has%20clinched%20232%20seats%2C%20defying%20exit%20poll%20predictions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717664580000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2F838a88i8_agniveer_625x300_06_June_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fagniveer-scheme-should-be-reconsidered-top-leader-from-nitish-kumars-party-5830061%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20the%20first%20sign%20that%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government's%20third%20term%20could%20be%20very%20different%20from%20the%20first%20two%2C%20a%20top%20Janata%20Dal%20United%20leader%20has%20said%20the%20party%20will%20seek%20a%20review%20of%20the%20Centre's%20Agnipath%20scheme%20for%20recruitment%20in%20the%20armed%20forces.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fagniveer-scheme-should-be-reconsidered-top-leader-from-nitish-kumars-party-5830061%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fagniveer-scheme-should-be-reconsidered-top-leader-from-nitish-kumars-party-5830061%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fagniveer-scheme-should-be-reconsidered-top-leader-from-nitish-kumars-party-5830061%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Hiker%20finds%20pipe%20feeding%20China's%20tallest%20waterfall%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717664246000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2Fbe30%2Flive%2Fb5ef5830-23d6-11ef-875c-47a7ad92adab.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fcp99l9gpzwgo%230%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20hiker%20posted%20a%20video%20showing%20the%20water%20flow%20of%20the%20fall%20was%20coming%20from%20a%20pipe%20built%20into%20the%20rock%20face.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A137%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fcp99l9gpzwgo%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fcp99l9gpzwgo.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fcp99l9gpzwgo.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Japan%20govt%20to%20launch%20dating%20app%20for%20this%20'gravest%20crisis%20country%20faces'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717664146000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-110763815%2Cimgsize-109136.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Ftechnology%2Ftech-news%2Fjapan-government-to-launch-dating-app-to-tackle-this-gravest-crisis-country-faces%2Farticleshow%2F110763816.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Tokyo%20City%20Hall%20launches%20'Tokyo%20Futari%20Story'%20initiative%20to%20combat%20loneliness%20and%20declining%20marriage%20rates%20in%20Japan.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20TECH%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Fancy%20Teacups%2C%20Rs%203.8%20Crore%20Pool%3A%205%20Times%20UK%20PM%20Rishi%20Sunak%20Came%20Under%20Fire%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EUK%20Prime%20Minster%20Rishi%20Sunak%20has%20been%20under%20scrutiny%20for%20various%20decisions%20and%20actions%20since%20he%20assumed%20the%20top%20post%20on%20October%2025%2C%202022.%20Despite%20his%20historic%20appointment%20as%20the%20first%20British-Asian%20PM%20and%20first%20Hindu%20to%20hold%20the%20office%2C%20Mr%20Sunak's%20tenure%20has%20not%20been%20without%20controversy.%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cstrong%3EHere%20are%20five%20times%20Rishi%20Sunak%20found%20himself%20in%20hot%20water%20after%20taking%20office%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cstrong%3EImmigrant%20visa%2C%20Graduate%20route%20visa%20policy%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnThe%20British%20Prime%20Minister%20faced%20backlash%20in%20May%202024%20for%20considering%20restrictions%20to%20the%20UK's%20post-study%20visa%2C%20which%20allows%20graduates%20to%20stay%20and%20work%20for%20up%20to%20two%20years%20after%20completing%20their%20degree.%20However%2C%20following%20strong%20opposition%20from%20key%20cabinet%20members%20and%20concerns%20raised%20about%20its%20impact%20on%20universities%20and%20the%20economy%2C%20Mr%20Sunak%20decided%20to%20abandon%20the%20radical%20plans.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnThe%20Graduate%20Route%20scheme%2C%20particularly%20popular%20among%20Indian%20students%2C%20will%20be%20kept%20under%20review%20while%20the%20UK%20government%20introduces%20measures%20to%20tighten%20student%20visa%20regulations.%20This%20decision%20comes%20after%20Chancellor%20Jeremy%20Hunt%2C%20Foreign%20Secretary%20David%20Cameron%2C%20Home%20Secretary%20James%20Cleverly%2C%20and%20Education%20Secretary%20Gillian%20Keegan%20voiced%20their%20opposition%2C%20keeping%20note%20of%20the%20significant%20contribution%20of%20Indian%20students%20to%20the%20UK's%20graduate%20visa%20numbers.%20Now%20Mr%20Sunak%20has%20planned%20to%20include%20setting%20a%20new%20cap%20on%20the%20number%20of%20visas%20annually.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cstrong%3EPost%20office%20scandal%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnIn%20January%202024%2C%20the%20UK%20Prime%20Minister%20proposed%20a%20law%20to%20help%20victims%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fuk-wales-67938713%C2%A0%5C%22%3EPost%20Office%20scandal%3C%2Fa%3E.%20This%20scandal%20involved%20hundreds%20of%20employees%2C%20who%20were%20wrongly%20accused%20because%20of%20problems%20with%20the%20software%20used%20by%20the%20Post%20Office.%20During%20a%20session%20of%20Prime%20Minister's%20Questions%2C%20Mr%20Sunak%20announced%20that%20the%20proposed%20law%20would%20offer%20an%20upfront%20payment%20of%20%C2%A375%2C000%20(%E2%82%B979%2C30%2C172)%20to%20former%20post%20office%20workers%20who%20were%20part%20of%20a%20legal%20case%20in%202019.%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnThis%20announcement%20came%20after%20the%20Metropolitan%20Police%20started%20investigating%20possible%20fraud%20related%20to%20the%20scandal.%20The%20scandal%20gained%20renewed%20attention%20because%20of%20a%20TV%20series%20called%20%26quot%3BMr.%20Bates%20vs%20the%20Post%20Office.%26quot%3B%20The%20scandal%2C%20which%20involved%20a%20software%20called%20Horizon%2C%20led%20to%20more%20than%20700%20sub-postmasters%20being%20wrongly%20accused.%20Some%20of%20these%20accusations%20were%20overturned%2C%20and%20the%20victims%20received%20compensation.%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnHowever%2C%20Noel%20Thomas%2C%20a%20former%20sub-postmaster%20ensnared%20in%20the%20scandal%2C%20was%20sceptical%20towards%20Rishi%20Sunak's%20latest%20plan.%20Mr%20Thomas%20had%20been%20jailed%20in%202006%20for%20false%20accounting%20after%20his%20accounts%20showed%20a%20%C2%A348%2C000%20(%E2%82%B951%2C24%2C653)%20shortfall.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnUpon%20learning%20about%20the%20new%20legislation%20proposed%20to%20overturn%20convictions%2C%20Mr%20Thomas%20stated%20that%20he%20was%20unconvinced%20until%20he%20saw%20the%20specifics%20of%20the%20plan%2C%20stating%20he%20had%20been%20promised%20a%20lot%20in%20the%20past%2C%20only%20for%20nothing%20to%20materialise.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cstrong%3EForeign%20students%20-%20English%20test%20scandal%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnIn%20March%202023%2C%20a%20group%20of%20international%20students%2C%20including%20many%20from%20India%2C%20wrote%20a%20petition%20to%20Mr%20Sunak%20over%20the%20revocation%20of%20their%20visas%20following%20an%20English%20test%20scandal%20dating%20back%20to%202014.%20The%20scandal%20involved%20cheating%20at%20UK%20testing%20centres%2C%20which%20led%20to%20a%20widespread%20crackdown%20and%20the%20expulsion%20of%20thousands%20of%20students.%20The%20petition%20called%20for%20fair%20treatment%2C%20transparent%20processes%2C%20and%20support%20for%20affected%20students%20navigating%20the%20aftermath.%20The%20students%20had%20wanted%20Rishi%20Sunak%20to%20help%20them%20clear%20their%20names.%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cstrong%3ESpent%20%E2%82%B93.8%20crore%20swimming%20pool%20amid%20drought%20in%20UK%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnJust%20a%20month%20before%20the%202022%20UK%20prime%20ministerial%20elections%2C%20Rishi%20Sunak%20found%20himself%20in%20the%20spotlight%20due%20to%20his%20lifestyle%20choices.%20Reports%20indicated%20that%20Mr%20Sunak%20had%20splurged%20approximately%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Frishi-sunak-in-hot-water-over-3-8-crores-pool-amid-drought-in-uk-report-3254655%C2%A0%5C%22%3E%E2%82%B93.8%20crore%20on%20a%20lavish%20swimming%20pool%3C%2Fa%3E%20within%20his%20mansion%20in%20North%20Yorkshire%2C%20amid%20concerns%20over%20drought%20and%20a%20severe%20heatwave%20gripping%20various%20parts%20of%20England%20at%20the%20time.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cstrong%3EAkshata%20Murty%20using%20fancy%20teacups%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnIn%202022%2C%20Rishi%20Sunak's%20wife%2C%20Akshata%20Murty%2C%20faced%20online%20criticism%20for%20using%20fancy%20teacups.%20Mrs%20Murty%20treated%20photographers%20outside%20their%20home%20with%20a%20tray%20of%20tea%20and%20biscuits.%20While%20her%20warm%20gesture%20was%20appreciated%20by%20many%2C%20it%20was%20the%20expensive%20cups%20that%20drew%20attention.%20The%20maker%20of%20the%20cups%2C%20designer%20Emma%20Lacey%2C%20confirmed%20on%20Twitter%20that%20they%20were%20from%20her%20'The%20Everyday%20Mug%20Range'%2C%20available%20in%2020%20colour%20variants%2C%20with%20a%20retail%20price%20of%20%C2%A338%20each%20(%E2%82%B9%203%2C625%20each).%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717663800000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Fgnu2sdn8_rishi-sunak-afp_625x300_23_May_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Ffancy-teacups-rs-3-8-crore-swimming-pool-5-times-rishi-sunak-came-under-fire-5830370%