%2020yo%20was%20staring%20at%20me%20continuously.%20I%20just%20pretended%20that%20I%20didn't%20see%20him%20staring%20at%20me%20and%20kept%20scrolling%20reels.%20After%20about%205-6%20minutes%20he%20started%20whistling%20and%20when%20I%20looked%20at%20him%20he%20winked%20and%20started%20to%20laugh.%20I%20was%20just%20stunned%20like%20wtf%20just%20happened%3F''%20she%20wrote.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0As%20she%20headed%20towards%20the%20washroom%2C%20the%20younger%20man%20followed%20her%2C%20whistling%20again.%20When%20the%20other%20man%20sensed%20something%20was%20wrong%2C%20he%20didn't%20admonish%20the%20younger%20man%20but%20said%20extremely%20awful%20things%20like%2C%20''%3Cem%3Edekhna%20hai%20toh%20dekho%20ye%20sab%20mat%20kro%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D%2C%20''%3Cem%3Edekhna%20ukhna%20chalta%20hai''%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0(If%20you%20want%20to%20look%2C%20just%20look.%20Don't%20do%20these%20things)%2C%20''%3Cem%3Edekh%20ke%20maza%20lo%20bas%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0(It's%20fine%20to%20look%2C%20just%20enjoy).''%20No%20one%20else%20intervened.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESee%20the%20post%20here%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-embed-height%3D%5C%22316%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reddit.com%2Fr%2Findianrailways%2Fcomments%2F1d8oz5i%2Fi_am_never_going_to_travel_alone_in_sleeper_class%2F%5C%22%3EI%20am%20never%20going%20to%20travel%20alone%20in%20sleeper%20class!!!!%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cnby%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reddit.com%2Fuser%2FEither_Ball_1407%2F%5C%22%3Eu%2FEither_Ball_1407%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reddit.com%2Fr%2Findianrailways%2F%5C%22%3Eindianrailways%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ordeal%20didn't%20end%20there.%20As%20she%20gathered%20her%20belongings%20to%20get%20off%20at%20her%20station%2C%20the%20young%20man%20asked%20for%20her%20phone%20number.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E''I%20ignored%20and%20walked%20as%20fast%20as%20I%20could%20to%20get%20out%20of%20the%20train.%20Luckily%20my%20father%20came%20inside%20and%20that%20was%20when%20I%20took%20a%20sigh%20of%20relief.%20Man%2C%20I%20just%20cried%20so%20hard%20after%20reaching%20home%20I%20was%20disgusted%20by%20their%20words%20%26quot%3B%20dekh%20ke%20mza%20ko%20na%20bas%26quot%3B%20wtf%20is%20mza%20lo%20man%3F%20I%20wish%20I%20had%20said%20something%20then%20but%20I%20was%20terrified.%20What%20if%20he%20does%20something%20and%20no%20one%20comes%20out%20to%20help%3F%20There's%20no%20way%20I%20am%20travelling%20alone%20in%20a%20sleeper%20class%20now.%20Never%20in%20my%20life!!!!''%20she%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeveral%20users%20sympathised%20with%20her%20and%20asked%20her%20to%20take%20action%20against%20the%20men.%20One%20user%20wrote%2C%20''Always%20better%20to%20video%20record%20all%20this%20discreetly%20as%20proof.%20And%20don't%20be%20scared%20of%20making%20a%20ruckus.%20And%20make%20sure%20you%20complain%20to%20TTE%20And%20RPF%20And%20throw%20these%20creeps%20out%20the%20train.''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20commented%2C%20''So%20sorry%20you%20had%20to%20experience%20this.%20It%20is%20individuals%20like%20these%20that%20can%20ruin%20and%20destroy%20a%20beautiful%20journey%20along%20with%20one's%20faith%20in%20society.%20I%20also%20want%20to%20mention%20that%20unfortunately%2C%20such%20incidents%20can%20also%20happen%20in%20an%20air-conditioned%20coach.%20Please%20keep%20phone%20numbers%20of%20RPF%20handy%20at%20all%20times%20and%20report%20any%20discomfort%20you%20have%20immediately.''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20third%20said%2C%20''The%20people%20who%20saw%20this%20and%20didn't%20do%20anything%20are%20equally%20as%20guilty%20as%20the%20ones%20who%20did%20it.%20Incidents%20like%20this%20makes%20me%20feel%20disgusted%20ngl.''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717662600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2F90nj1tso_train_625x300_06_June_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%