BDue%20to%20my%20differing%20view%20on%20leadership%20accountability%20and%20succession%20planning%2C%20I%20will%20be%20resigning%20from%20the%20Board%20effective%20June%203rd%2C%202024.%26quot%3B%20The%20board%20of%20VIP%20Industries%20is%20led%20by%20Dilip%20Piramal%20as%20Chairman%20of%20the%20Rs%202%2C250-crore%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENisaba%20Godrej%20was%20reappointed%20to%20the%20board%20of%20VIP%20Industries%20in%20April%202021%20as%20an%20independent%20director%20and%20her%20term%20was%20ending%20on%20March%2031%2C%202026.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20attended%20all%20five%20meetings%20held%20in%20FY23%20and%20has%20voluntarily%20waived%20off%20receipt%20of%20sitting%20fees%20for%20any%20meetings%20attended%20by%20her%2C%20said%20the%20annual%20report%20of%20the%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20her%20resignation%20letter%20to%20the%20chairman%20of%20VIP%20Industries%2C%20she%20further%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BVIP%20Industries%20is%20a%20wonderful%20company%2C%20a%20creator%20of%20the%20luggage%20category%20in%20India%20and%20the%20market%20leader%20and%20I%20wish%20the%20company%20much%20success%20in%20the%20years%20to%20come.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20alumnus%20of%20Wharton%20School%20and%20Harvard%20Business%20School%2C%20Nisaba%20Godrej%20is%20the%20director%20of%20another%20Godrej%20group%20firm%20Godrej%20Agrovet.%20Besides%2C%20she%20is%20also%20an%20independent%20director%20of%20Bharti%20Airtel%20and%20Mahindra%20and%20Mahindra.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVIP%20Industries%2C%20which%20has%20a%20market%20capitalisation%20of%20Rs%206%2C900%20crore%2C%20competes%20with%20Samsonite%20and%20Safari%20Industries%20in%20the%20premium%20and%20mass%20segment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20company%2C%20which%20owns%20brands%20such%20as%20Aristocrat%2C%20VIP%2C%20Carlton%2C%20Skybags%20and%20Caprese%2C%20had%20a%20market%20share%20of%2056%20per%20cent%20in%20the%20branded%20luggage%20segment%20in%20FY24.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20company%20is%20facing%20stiff%20competition%20from%20rivals%20and%20its%20market%20share%20is%20gradually%20reducing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20financial%20year%20ended%20March%202024%2C%20VIP%20Industries'%20revenue%20from%20operations%20stood%20at%20Rs%202%2C245%20crore%2C%20up%207.82%20per%20cent%20year%20on%20year.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717661700000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2F2ggd00go_nisaba-godrej-godrej-group_625x300_06_June_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fgodrej-consumer-executive-chairperson-nisaba-godrej-resigns-from-vip-industries-board-citing-differences-5830000%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Godrej%20Consumer's%20executive%20chairperson%20Nisaba%20Godrej%20has%20resigned%20as%20an%20independent%20director%20from%20the%20board%20of%20luggage%20and%20travel%20accessories%20maker%20VIP%20Industries%2C%20citing%20differences%20over%20leadership%20accountability%20and%20succession%20planning.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fgodrej-consumer-executive-chairperson-nisaba-godrej-resigns-from-vip-industries-board-citing-differences-5830000%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fgodrej-consumer-executive-chairperson-nisaba-godrej-resigns-from-vip-industries-board-citing-differences-5830000%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fgodrej-consumer-executive-chairperson-nisaba-godrej-resigns-from-vip-industries-board-citing-differences-5830000%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22OPPO%20F27%20Pro%20Plus%2C%20India's%20first%20IP69-rated%20phone%2C%20set%20to%20launch%20on%20June%2013%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22