%20morning.%20The%20image%20went%20viral%20long%20before%20the%20flight%20landed%20in%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20optics%20of%20that%20encounter%20were%20not%20lost%20on%20anyone%2C%20least%20of%20all%20Nitish%20Kumar%2C%20who%2C%20after%20multiple%20flip-flops%2C%20is%20determined%20to%20extract%20his%20pound%20of%20flesh%20as%20one%20of%20the%20two%20main%20allies%20propping%20up%20Narendra%20Modi's%20third%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20NDA%20won%20a%20third%20consecutive%20term%20in%20the%20national%20election.%20The%20BJP%20emerged%20as%20the%20single%20largest%20party%20with%20240%20seats%20but%20fell%20short%20of%20a%20majority%20in%20Lok%20Sabha.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20sources%2C%20soon%20after%20the%20flight%20took%20off%2C%20Nitish%20Kumar%20turned%20to%20Tejashwi%20Yadav%20and%20initiated%20conversation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Bihar%20Chief%20Minister%20reportedly%20showed%20his%20inked%20index%20finger%20and%20asked%20his%20former%20deputy%2C%20%26quot%3BWhat%20about%20you%3F%26quot%3B%20Tejashwi%20responded%20by%20holding%20up%20his%20own%20inked%20finger.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENitish%20Kumar%20reportedly%20urged%20Tejashwi%20to%20join%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20woman%20seated%20next%20to%20the%20chief%20minister%20was%20asked%20to%20swap%20seats%20with%20Tejashwi%20Yadav.%20Retired%20bureaucrat%20Shishir%20Sinha%2C%20travelling%20with%20Nitish%20Kumar%2C%20reportedly%20facilitated%20the%20seat-switch.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETejashwi%2C%20originally%20sitting%20with%20RJD%20Rajya%20Sabha%20member%20Sanjay%20Yadav%2C%20sat%20next%20to%20Nitish%20Kumar%20for%20almost%20an%20hour%2C%20say%20sources.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20was%20no%20political%20discussion%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20sources%20claimed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETejashwi%20told%20reporters%3A%20%26quot%3BWe%20greeted%20each%20other%2C%20I%20was%20allotted%20the%20seat%20behind%20him%20but%20he%20saw%20me%20and%20called%20me%20to%20sit%20with%20him.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENitish%20Kumar%20and%20Tejashwi%20Yadav%20have%20not%20revealed%20their%20in-flight%20conversation%2C%20allowing%20a%20free%20run%20to%20theories%20as%20each%20attended%20separate%20meetings%20in%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Wednesday%20evening%2C%20Nitish%20Kumar%20attended%20an%20NDA%20meeting%20and%20pledged%20support%20to%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20the%20BJP.%20Negotiations%20are%20still%20open%20on%20ministries%20and%20other%20demands%20laid%20down%20by%20the%20Janata%20Dal%20United%20(JDU)%20in%20exchange%20for%20their%20support.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETejashwi%20Yadav%20joined%20a%20meeting%20of%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20held%20last%20evening.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717661100000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2F3hbi7mvo_nitish-tejashwi-flight_625x300_05_June_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Finside-story-of-nitish-kumar-tejashwi-yadavs-in-flight-meeting-5829826%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Nitish%20Kumar%20and%20Tejashwi%20Yadav's%20meeting%20on%20a%20flight%20to%20Delhi%20provoked%20a%20torrent%20of%20speculation%20as%20power%20negotiations%20dominated%20meetings%20in%20the%20capital%20of%20the%20BJP-led%20NDA%20and%20the%20opposition%20INDIA%20bloc.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Finside-story-of-nitish-kumar-tejashwi-yadavs-in-flight-meeting-5829826%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Finside-story-of-nitish-kumar-tejashwi-yadavs-in-flight-meeting-5829826%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Finside-story-of-nitish-kumar-tejashwi-yadavs-in-flight-meeting-5829826%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Sethupathi%20says%20you%20can%20never%20tell%20if%20SRK%20is%20sick%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717660863000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-110762041%2Cimgsize-43336.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fvijay-sethupathi-on-shah-rukh-khan-you-cant-tell-if-hes-ill-until-he-says%2Farticleshow%2F110762041.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F110762041.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3ELast%20year%2C%20Tamil%20actor%20Vijay%20Sethupathi%20made%20a%20notable%20debut%20in%20the%20Hindi%20film%20industry%20with%20the%20series%20%26quot%3BFarzi%26quot%3B%20and%20his%20role%20in%20Shah%20Rukh%20Khan%E2%80%99s%20%26quot%3BJawan.%26quot%3B%20His%20latest%20Bollywood%20release%20is%20%26quot%3BMerry%20Christmas%2C%26quot%3B%20starring%20Katrina%20Kaif%20and%20directed%20by%20Sriram%20Raghavan.%20In%20a%20recent%20interview%2C%20Vijay%20shared%20his%20special%20experience%20working%20with%20Shah%20Rukh%20Khan%20in%20%26quot%3BJawan%26quot%3B%20and%20expressed%20gratitude%20for%20SRK's%20praise.%20He%20mentioned%20no%20longer%20wanting%20to%20play%20villainous%20roles%2C%20indicating%20a%20shift%20in%20his%20career%20focus.%20Vijay%20noted%20learning%20from%20everyone%20he%20works%20with%2C%20highlighting%20Shah%20Rukh%20Khan's%20unwavering%20energy%20even%20when%20unwell.%20Compliments%20from%20Rajinikanth%20and%20Vijay%20also%20made%20him%20feel%20appreciated.%20Having%20played%20the%20antagonist%20in%20%26quot%3BJawan%2C%26quot%3B%20Vijay%20now%20aims%20to%20focus%20on%20romantic%20films.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20Entertainment%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fvijay-sethupathi-on-shah-rukh-khan-you-cant-tell-if-hes-ill-until-he-says%2Farticleshow%2F110762041.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BJoined%20Pakistan%20After%20IPL%26quot%3B%3A%20India's%20WC-Winning%20Coach%20Lambasted%20By%20Great%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EBabar%20Azam%20has%20a%20long%20way%20to%20go%20before%20becoming%20a%20captain%20who%20can%20handle%20pressure%2C%20said%20former%20Pakistan%20skipper%20Rashid%20Latif%2C%20declaring%20that%20India%20would%20be%20favourites%20against%20his%20country%20owing%20to%20a%20more%20balanced%20squad%20when%20the%20two%20sides%20clash%20in%20the%20T20%20World%20Cup%20on%20Sunday.%20The%20India-Pakistan%20showdown%2C%20to%20be%20held%20in%20New%20York%2C%20is%20one%20of%20the%20most%20eagerly-awaited%20games%20of%20the%20ongoing%20tournament%20being%20co-hosted%20by%20the%20USA%20and%20the%20West%20Indies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B...the%20focus%20is%20on%20the%20game%20on%20June%209%20against%20India.%20Babar%20(Pakistan%20captain)%20will%20be%20under%20a%20lot%20of%20pressure%20because%20of%20the%20game%20against%20India%20rather%20than%20performing%20in%20the%20World%20Cup%2C%26quot%3B%20the%2055-year-old%20former%20wicketkeeper-batter%20told%20PTI%20videos%20in%20an%20exclusive%20interview.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20he%20has%20to%20learn%20to%20carry%20pressure%2C%20he%20should%20learn%20that%20from%20Virat%20and%20Rohit.%20They%20know%20how%20to%20carry%20the%20game.%20As%20a%20batter%20Babar%20is%20one%20of%20the%20best%20but%20as%20a%20captain%20and%20leader%2C%20there's%20a%20lot%20that%20he%20needs%20to%20learn%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELatif%20said%20India%20have%20superior%20spinners%20and%20based%20on%20current%20form%2C%20Rohit%20Sharma's%20men%20are%20favourites%20for%20a%20win%20on%20Sunday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BKuldeep%20Yadav%20is%20that%20one%20player%20who%20if%20remains%20fit%20for%20India%20throughout%20the%20World%20Cup%2C%20he%20can%20cause%20trouble%20for%20batters.%20He%20is%20India's%20key%20bowler%20and%20also%20a%20key%20to%20success.%20Given%20the%20current%20form%20and%20stats%20definitely%20India%20has%20an%20advantage%20ahead%20of%20June%209%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELatif%20also%20pointed%20out%20that%20the%20Pakistan's%20preparedness%20is%20nowhere%20close%20to%20being%20as%20good%20as%20it%20was%20during%20its%20strong%20performances%20in%20the%202021%20and%202022%20editions%2C%20when%20the%20team%20reached%20the%20finals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Pakistan%20team%20plays%20well%20in%20the%20ICC%20tournaments%20but%20the%20team%20doesn't%20look%20as%20prepared%20as%20they%20were%20in%202021%20and%202022.%20The%20damage%20happened%20after%20the%20last%20ODI%20World%20Cup%20with%20changes%20in%20captaincy%2C%20the%20selection%20committee%2C%20and%20players%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20explained.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20team%20doesn't%20know%20who%20their%20openers%20will%20be%20and%20what%20they%20have%20tried%20has%20failed%20miserably%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20pointed%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELatif%20lamented%20the%20decline%20of%20Pakistan's%20bowling%2C%20especially%20the%20pacers.%20He%20blamed%20poor%20fitness%20for%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20lot%20of%20bowlers%20like%20Shaheen%2C%20Naseem%2C%20Rauf%2C%20Shadab%20came%20back%20from%20injury%20and%20now%20Imad%20Wasim%20is%20injured.%20The%20biggest%20issue%20has%20been%20the%20fitness%20of%20the%20bowlers%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFormer%20greats%20like%20Wasim%20Akram%2C%20Waqar%20Younis%2C%20Mohammad%20Asif%20were%20way%20fitter%20than%20them%20and%20never%20used%20to%20miss%20any%20Tests%20or%20ODIs.%20But%20these%20guys%2C%20despite%20playing%20shorter%20formats%2C%20don't%20have%20adequate%20fitness%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20criticised%20the%20selection%20of%20bowlers%20who%20play%20similar%20roles%20in%20the%20side.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B...they%20bring%20back%20Mohammad%20Amir%20and%20Imad%20Wasim.%20Earlier%20when%20these%20two%20bowlers%20used%20to%20play%20for%20Pakistan%20and%20in%20the%20PSL%2C%20they%20used%20to%20bowl%20the%20early%20overs%20between%201-4.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNow%2C%20Rauf%20and%20Shaheen%20perform%20the%20same%20role%2C%20if%20you%20have%20four%20bowlers%20with%20the%20same%20role%2C%20who%20will%20bowl%20in%20the%20middle%20overs%3F%26quot%3B%20he%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20lauded%20India%20for%20getting%20their%20bowling%20combination%20right.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLook%20at%20India%2C%20they%20have%20got%20Kuldeep%2C%20Axar%2C%20Jadeja%20and%20Chahal%20who%20can%20bowl%20in%20the%20middle%20and%20also%20the%20early%20overs.%20Pakistan%20couldn't%20develop%20Abrar%20Ahmed%20much.%20If%20Shadab%20Khan%20goes%20for%20runs%20in%20the%20middle%20overs%2C%20Pakistan%20doesn't%20have%20a%20lot%20of%20cover%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELatif%20also%20questioned%20the%20timing%20of%20South%20African%20Gary%20Kirsten's%20appointment%20as%20Pakistan%20coach.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20timing%20of%20his%20joining%20is%20very%20wrong.%20He%20joined%20the%20team%20on%20May%2019%20after%20the%20IPL%20season%20for%20Gujarat%20Titans%20ended%2C%26quot%3B%20Latif%20pointed%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20only%20knows%20players%20by%20their%20names%2C%20but%20when%20you%20are%20going%20to%20the%20World%20Cup%20then%20you%20at%20least%20need%20to%20have%20spent%20at%20least%20a%20year%20with%20the%20players.%20He%20did%20not%20get%20this%20time%20and%20the%20Pakistan%20board%20is%20to%20blame%20for%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20Virat%20Kohli%2C%20Latif%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BVirat%20has%20a%20lot%20of%20fans%20in%20Pakistan%20and%20also%20the%20players%20playing%20are%20his%20fans.%20Like%20I%20also%20say%20this%20whenever%20Sachin%20used%20to%20play%20earlier%2C%20I%20never%20wanted%20him%20to%20get%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20world%20was%20paying%20to%20watch%20him%20bat%20but%20I%20was%20sitting%20behind%20the%20stumps%20and%20enjoying%20it%20for%20free%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20recalled%20on%20a%20lighter%20note.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BVirat%20Kohli%20is%20a%20different%20player...Virat%20is%20a%20different%20player%20after%20this%20IPL%E2%80%A6It%20will%20be%20really%20interesting%20to%20see%20where%20he%20bats%20in%20this%20World%20Cup.%26quot%3B%20Kohli%20opened%20with%20Rohit%20in%20India's%20opener%20against%20Ireland.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELatif%20said%20even%20Babar%20can%20grow%20in%20stature%20but%20he%20needs%20a%20better%20team%20around%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBabar%20is%20a%20great%20player%20but%20doesn't%20have%20a%20lot%20of%20players%20to%20support%20him.%20Virat%20definitely%20has%20an%20advantage%20because%20the%20players%20are%20around%20him.%20But%20Pakistan%20lacks%20that%20cushion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBabar%20only%20has%20Rizwan%20and%20occasionally%20the%20support%20of%20Fakhar%20Zaman.%20Babar's%20quality%20is%20way%20above%20his%20teammates%20and%20I%20think%20this%20acts%20as%20a%20disadvantage%20for%20him.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717660500000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Ff8quv668_babar-azam-and-gary-kirsten-twitter_625x300_06_June_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ft20-world-cup-2024%2Flearn-from-virat-kohli-rohit-sharma-pakistan-great-tears-into-babar-azam-ahead-of-india-clash-5829756%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Babar%20Azam%20and%20his%20team%20find%20themselves%20in%20the%20line%20of%20fire%20right%20before%20the%20T20%20World%20Cup%202024%20clash%20against%20India.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ft20-world-cup-2024%2Flearn-from-virat-kohli-rohit-sharma-pakistan-great-tears-into-babar-a