logy%2Fgadgets%2Fvivo-x-fold-3-pro-launched-in-india-with-gemini-ai-features-price-specs-124060600379_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Ftechnology%2Fgadgets%2Fvivo-x-fold-3-pro-launched-in-india-with-gemini-ai-features-price-specs-124060600379_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Modi%203.0%3A%20BJP%20Likely%20To%20Keep%20Top%20Ministries%2C%20Allies%20Push%20For%20More%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ETwo%20days%20after%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%20results%20denied%20a%20clear%20majority%20to%20the%20BJP%2C%20its%20allies%20in%20NDA%20have%20started%20bargaining%20hard%20for%20plum%20posts%20at%20the%20Centre.%20The%20BJP%2C%20however%2C%20is%20not%20in%20the%20mood%20to%20let%20go%20of%20key%20miniseries%20and%20roles%2C%20sources%20have%20said.%20With%20the%20single%20largest%20party%20well%20short%20of%20the%20magic%20figure%2C%20NDA%20allies%20are%20now%20on%20a%20tight%20deadline%20to%20reach%20a%20consensus%20as%20plans%20are%20afoot%20to%20hold%20the%20swearing%20in%20ceremony%20of%20the%20third%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%20this%20weekend.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20four%20allies%20whose%20support%20is%20critical%20for%20the%20BJP%20to%20reach%20majority%20are%20N%20Chandrabau%20Naidu's%20TDP%2C%20which%20has%20won%2016%20seats%2C%20Nitish%20Kumar's%20JDU%20(12)%2C%20Eknath%20Shinde's%20Shiv%20Sena%20(7)%20and%20Chirag%20Paswan's%20Lok%20Janshakti%20Party-Ram%20Vilas%20(5).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EN%20Chandrababu%20Naidu%20and%20Nitish%20Kumar%2C%20both%20coalition-era%20veterans%2C%20have%20emerged%20kingmakers%20in%20this%20election%20and%20are%20learnt%20to%20have%20demanded%20plum%20roles%20at%20the%20Centre%20for%20their%20support.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETDP%2C%20it%20is%20learnt%2C%20has%20also%20sought%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20Speaker's%20post%2C%20while%20JDU%20sources%20said%20they%20may%20press%20for%20a%20Common%20Minimum%20Programme%20for%20the%20NDA%20government%20and%20hope%20that%20a%20coordination%20committee%20formed%20for%20its%20implementation%20is%20led%20by%20Nitish%20Kumar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%2C%20sources%20said%2C%20is%20not%20ready%20to%20give%20away%20the%20Speaker's%20role%20and%20TDP%20may%20be%20offered%20a%20Deputy%20Speaker%20post.%20JDU%20holds%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20Deputy%20Chairman%20post%20anyway.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20another%20big%20change.%20The%20Narendra%20Modi%20governments%20formed%20after%20the%202014%20and%202019%20elections%20had%20only%20symbolic%20representation%20of%20allies%20because%20the%20BJP%20had%20absolute%20majority%20on%20its%20own.%20But%20this%20time%2C%20the%20BJP%20may%20have%20to%20distribute%20ministerial%20berths%20in%20proportion%20to%20seats%20won%20by%20each%20ally.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%2C%20however%2C%20is%20not%20keen%20on%20accommodating%20allies%20in%20four%20key%20ministries%20that%20come%20under%20the%20Cabinet%20Committee%20on%20Security%20--%20defence%2C%20finance%2C%20home%20affairs%20and%20external%20affairs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20will%20also%20not%20want%20to%20let%20go%20of%20portfolios%20that%20are%20critical%20to%20its%20infrastructure%20push%2C%20such%20as%20road%20transport%20and%20highways%2C%20or%20its%20welfare%20agenda.%20Among%20the%20BJP's%20promises%20in%20the%20run-up%20to%20the%20election%20was%20support%20to%20four%20%26quot%3Bcastes%26quot%3B%20identified%20by%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20--%20the%20poor%2C%20women%2C%20youth%20and%20farmers.%20The%20BJP%20will%20be%20looking%20to%20retain%20control%20in%20portfolios%20relating%20to%20these%20groups.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConstruction%20of%20roads%20and%20highways%20in%20the%20past%2010%20years%20of%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%20has%20received%20appreciation.%20Led%20by%20Nitin%20Gadkari%2C%20this%20push%20has%20enhanced%20connectivity%20to%20remote%20areas.%20The%20BJP%20would%20not%20want%20to%20lose%20momentum%20by%20giving%20charge%20to%20one%20of%20its%20allies%2C%20sources%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20key%20portfolio%20is%20the%20Railways.%20While%20JDU%20sources%20have%20said%20they%20are%20keen%20to%20get%20the%20Railways%20ministry%20charge%2C%20held%20by%20Nitish%20Kumar%20in%20the%20past%2C%20voices%20in%20the%20BJP%20argue%20that%20key%20reforms%20are%20underway%20in%20this%20sector%20and%20any%20disruption%20may%20stall%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20past%20two%20Narendra%20Modi%20governments%2C%20allies%20received%20roles%20in%20relatively%20low-key%20portfolios%20such%20as%20food%20processing%20and%20heavy%20industries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20this%20time%2C%20the%20BJP%20may%20have%20to%20agree%20to%20some%20of%20its%20allies'%20demands%2C%20as%20they%20do%20not%20have%20a%20majority%20on%20their%20own.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20sources%2C%20JDU%20may%20be%20offered%20portfolios%20such%20as%20panchayati%20raj%2C%20rural%20development%2C%20while%20TDP%20may%20get%20civil%20aviation%20and%20steel.%20The%20BJP%20may%2C%20however%2C%20try%20to%20accommodate%20allies'%20MPs%20in%20Minister%20of%20State%20roles%20in%20big-ticket%20ministries%20such%20as%20Finance%20and%20Defence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOther%20portfolios%20the%20BJP%20may%20be%20open%20to%20handing%20over%20to%20portfolios%20include%20tourism%2C%20skill%20development%2C%20science%20and%20technology%20and%20earth%20sciences.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717660140000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Fro2u1ta_modi-nitish-naidu_625x300_06_June_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F2024-lok-sabha-election-results-bjp-short-of-majority-but-not-keen-to-lose-control-in-modi-3-0-sources-5829943%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Two%20days%20after%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%20results%20denied%20a%20clear%20majority%20to%20the%20BJP%2C%20its%20allies%20in%20NDA%20have%20started%20bargaining%20hard%20for%20plum%20posts%20at%20the%20Centre.%20The%20BJP%2C%20however%2C%20is%20not%20in%20the%20mood%20to%20let%20go%20of%20ke