0Hamas's%20October%207%20attack%20on%20southern%20Israel%2C%20which%20resulted%20in%20the%20deaths%20of%201%2C194%20people%2C%20mostly%20civilians%2C%20according%20to%20an%20AFP%20tally%20based%20on%20Israeli%20official%20figures.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECombatants%20also%20took%20251%20hostages%2C%20120%20of%20whom%20remain%20in%20Gaza%2C%20including%2041%20the%20army%20says%20are%20dead.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsrael's%20ensuing%20bombardment%20and%20ground%20offensive%20have%20killed%20at%20least%2036%2C586%20people%20in%20Gaza%2C%20also%20mostly%20civilians%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Hamas-run%20territory's%20health%20ministry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsrael%20has%20faced%20growing%20diplomatic%20isolation%20over%20its%20conduct%20of%20the%20war%2C%20with%20cases%20against%20it%20before%20two%20international%20courts%2C%20and%20several%20European%20governments%20recognising%20a%20Palestinian%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsrael%20has%20frequently%20accused%20Hamas%20and%20its%20allies%20in%20Gaza%20of%20using%20schools%2C%20health%20facilities%20and%20other%20civilian%20infrastructure%20as%20operational%20centres%20--%20charges%20the%20combatants%20deny.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUNRWA%2C%20which%20coordinates%20nearly%20all%20aid%20to%20Gaza%2C%20has%20been%20in%20crisis%20since%20January%2C%20when%20Israel%20accused%20about%20a%20dozen%20of%20its%2013%2C000%20employees%20in%20the%20territory%20of%20being%20involved%20in%20the%20October%207%20attack.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIts%20chief%2C%20Philippe%20Lazzarini%2C%20said%20last%20week%20that%20Israel%20%26quot%3Bmust%20stop%20its%20campaign%20against%20UNRWA%26quot%3B%20in%20an%20opinion%20article%20published%20by%20the%20New%20York%20Times.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ESticking%20points%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20latest%20strike%20came%20as%20US%2C%20Qatari%20and%20Egyptian%20mediators%20resumed%20talks%20Wednesday%20to%20try%20to%20secure%20a%20truce%20and%20hostage%20release%20deal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUS%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20last%20week%20outlined%20what%20he%20called%20a%20three-phase%20Israeli%20plan%20to%20halt%20the%20fighting%20for%20six%20weeks%20while%20hostages%20held%20by%20combatants%20in%20Gaza%20are%20exchanged%20for%20Palestinian%20prisoners%20and%20aid%20is%20stepped%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EG7%20powers%20and%20Arab%20states%20have%20backed%20the%20proposal%20announced%20by%20Biden%2C%20although%20sticking%20points%20remain%20--%20Hamas%20insists%20on%20a%20permanent%20truce%20and%20full%20Israeli%20withdrawal%2C%20demands%20that%20Israel%20has%20flatly%20rejected.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20source%20with%20knowledge%20of%20the%20negotiations%20confirmed%20to%20AFP%20that%20a%20meeting%20took%20place%20on%20Wednesday%20%26quot%3Bbetween%20the%20Qatari%20prime%20minister%20and%20head%20of%20Egyptian%20intelligence%20with%20Hamas%20in%20Qatari%20capital%20Doha%20to%20discuss%20a%20deal%20for%20a%20truce%20in%20Gaza%20and%20the%20exchange%20of%20hostages%20and%20prisoners%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBiden%20has%20urged%20Hamas%20to%20accept%20the%20deal%20and%20has%20deployed%20CIA%20chief%20Bill%20Burns%20to%20Qatar%2C%20where%20the%20group's%20political%20bureau%20is%20based%2C%20for%20a%20renewed%20push%20after%20months%20of%20negotiations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20source%20said%20Burns%20would%20%26quot%3Bcontinue%20working%20with%20mediators%20on%20reaching%20an%20agreement%20between%20Hamas%20and%20Israel%20on%20a%20ceasefire%20in%20Gaza%20and%20the%20release%20of%20hostages%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBiden%20earlier%20told%20Qatar's%20emir%20that%20%26quot%3BHamas%20is%20now%20the%20only%20obstacle%20to%20a%20complete%20ceasefire%26quot%3B%2C%20and%20%26quot%3Bconfirmed%20Israel's%20readiness%20to%20move%20forward%26quot%3B%20with%20the%20terms%20he%20set%20out%20last%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20senior%20Hamas%20official%20in%20Beirut%20on%20Tuesday%20accused%20Israel%20of%20seeking%20%26quot%3Bendless%26quot%3B%20negotiations%20and%20reiterated%20the%20group's%20position%20rejecting%20any%20deal%20that%20excludes%20a%20permanent%20ceasefire.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHamas%20leader%20Ismail%20Haniyeh%20said%20his%20group%20would%20%26quot%3Bdeal%20seriously%20and%20positively%26quot%3B%20with%20any%20offer%20meeting%20those%20demands.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMuhammad%20al-Najjar%2C%20a%2035-year-old%20man%20from%20northern%20Gaza%20twice%20displaced%20by%20the%20war%2C%20told%20AFP%3A%20%26quot%3BWe%20just%20want%20to%20solve%20and%20end%20the%20catastrophic%20situation%20that%20we%20are%20living.%20What%20matters%20to%20us%20is%20that%20the%20war%20made%20us%20exhausted%2C%20destroyed%20us%20and%20destroyed%20everything%20in%20our%20lives.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EJerusalem%20march%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Jerusalem%2C%20Israeli%20police%20deployed%203%2C000%20officers%20ahead%20of%20the%20annual%20march%20by%20right-wingers%20commemorating%20Israel's%20capture%20of%20the%20Old%20City%20in%20the%201967%20Arab-Israeli%20war.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20march%20draws%20Israeli%20religious%20ultranationalists%20and%20Zionist%20youth%20groups%2C%20and%20leads%20through%20the%20city's%20Muslim%20Quarter%20to%20the%20Western%20Wall.%20It%20has%20been%20a%20lightning%20rod%20for%20Israeli-Palestinian%20tensions%20in%20recent%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETensions%20have%20also%20spiralled%20elsewhere%20in%20the%20region%20between%20Israel%20and%20its%20allies%20on%20the%20one%20hand%2C%20and%20Iran-backed%20armed%20groups%20in%20Lebanon%2C%20Iraq%2C%20Syria%20and%20Yemen%20on%20the%20other.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Israeli%20army%20and%20Lebanon's%20Hezbollah%20movement%20have%20traded%20near-daily%20cross-border%20fire%2C%20causing%20deaths%2C%20forcing%20mass%20evacuations%20and%20igniting%20wildfires%20on%20both%20sides.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrime%20Minister%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu%20said%20on%20Wednesday%20that%20Israel%20was%20%26quot%3Bprepared%20for%20a%20very%20intense%20operation%26quot%3B%20along%20the%20border%20with%20Lebanon%20and%20that%20%26quot%3Bone%20way%20or%20another%2C%20we%20will%20restore%20security%20to%20the%20north%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20United%20States%20appeared%20to%20warn%20Israel%20against%20taking%20action%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20with%20the%20State%20Department%20saying%20that%20any%20%26quot%3Bescalation%26quot%3B%20there%20would%20risk%20Israeli%20security.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20violence%20since%20early%20October%20has%20killed%20at%20least%20455%20people%20in%20Lebanon%2C%20mostly%20fighters%20but%20including%2088%20civilians%2C%20according%20to%20an%20AFP%20tally.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20Israeli%20side%2C%20the%20army%20says%20at%20least%2014%20soldiers%20and%2011%20civilians%20have%20been%20killed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717658940000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Fau27kv3g_un-school-strikes-gaza_625x300_06_June_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2F30-dead-in-strikes-on-gaza-school-israel-says-it-was-targetting-terrorists-5829331%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Israeli%20military%20said%20Thursday%20it%20had%20carried%20out%20a%20deadly%20strike%20on%20a%20UN%20school%20in%20Gaza%20that%20it%20said%20housed%20a%20Hamas%20compound%2C%20with%20the%20militant%20group%20saying%20the%20attack%20killed%20at%20least%2027%20people.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2F30-dead-in-strikes-on-gaza-school-israel-says-it-was-targetting-terrorists-5829331%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2F30-dead-in-strikes-on-gaza-school-israel-says-it-was-targetting-terrorists-5829331%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%2