%3E%5Cn%3Col%20start%3D%5C%2213%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EHighlighting%20the%20challenges%20on%20the%20terrace%20and%20balconies%2C%20Harish%20mentions%20that%20residents%20will%20have%20to%20bear%20metre%20and%20wiring%20expenses%20that%20can%20go%20up%20to%20Rs%201%20lakh.%20Using%20balconies%20could%20not%20be%20very%20feasible%20if%20the%20energy%20generation%20will%20be%20small-scale%20compared%20to%20the%20requirement.%20In%20the%20case%20of%20balconies%2C%20there%20are%20safety%20risks%20from%20extreme%20weather%20events%20like%20lightning%20strikes%2C%20strong%20winds%2C%20and%20cyclones%20that%20can%20damage%20the%20panels.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Col%20start%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EKiran%20points%20out%20that%20there%E2%80%99s%20a%20lot%20of%20paperwork%20involved%20with%20the%20concerned%20electricity%20boards.%20For%20instance%2C%20the%20contract%20term%20with%20the%20concerned%20electricity%20provider%20and%20the%20subsidy.%20The%20service%20provider%20and%20the%20solar%20installation%20companies%20will%20help%20do%20the%20paperwork%20but%20ensure%20that%20you%20keep%20a%20copy%20of%20all%20the%20documents.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Col%20start%3D%5C%2215%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EHe%20further%20asks%20residents%20to%20consider%20the%20maths%20on%20subsequent%20savings.%20If%20your%20monthly%20power%20bill%20is%20Rs%202%2C500%20in%20a%202BHK%2C%20then%20you%20will%20recover%20the%20cost%20of%20solar%20installation%20in%2010%20years%20(assuming%20rooftop%20cable%20wiring%20expenses%20in%20addition%20to%20inverter%20and%20installation%20costs%20totaling%20Rs%203%20lakh).%20It%20does%20not%20make%20sense%20if%20the%20monthly%20bill%20is%20Rs%201%2C000-1%2C200%20and%20tenants%20move%20out%20shortly%20after.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Edited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande%3B%20Photo%20credit%3A%20Adobe%20stock%20images%2C%20Bhoomi%20Arkade%2C%20and%20Palash%20Co-Operative%20Housing%20Society)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A17