nothing%20that%20can%20beat%20this%20snack%2C%20laced%20with%20%3Cem%3Echutney%3C%2Fem%3E.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E7.%20Swati%20Snacks%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20belly%20of%20Mumbai%E2%80%99s%20Tardeo%20lies%20an%20eatery%20that%20has%20stuck%20to%20one%20philosophy%3A%20home%20food%20is%20the%20best%20food.%20Minakshi%20Jhaveri%2C%20a%20single%20mother%20started%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F252694%2Fswati-snacks-minakshi-jhaveri-iconic-eatery-india-inspiring-single-mother-success-stories-authentic-homemade-food-chaat-gop94%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESwati%20Snacks%3C%2Fa%3E%20without%20any%20prior%20business%20acumen%2C%20serving%20four%20items%20%E2%80%94%20%3Cem%3Esev%20puri%2C%20bhel%20puri%2C%20ragda%20pattice%20and%20pani%20puri%3C%2Fem%3E%20%E2%80%94%20priced%20at%20four%20%3Cem%3Eaanas%3C%2Fem%3E%20(a%20currency%20unit%20used%20in%20British%20India).%20But%20with%20this%20simple%20formula%2C%20she%20created%20history%20and%20a%20multi-crore%20brand.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20son%20Anand%20once%20shared%20with%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CMy%20mother%20treated%20all%20her%20customers%20the%20way%20she%20would%20guests%20who%20visit%20our%20home.%20For%20a%20guest%2C%20who%20is%20equivalent%20to%20God%2C%20you%20will%20prepare%20the%20food%20with%20the%20best%20intentions%20and%20a%20positive%20attitude%2C%20which%20automatically%20reflects%20in%20the%20taste.%20While%20growing%20up%2C%20I%20watched%20her%20spend%20that%20extra%20hour%20just%20so%20she%20could%20inspect%20the%20ingredients%20multiple%20times%2C%20or%20even%20walk%20kilometres%20to%20procure%20fresh%20ingredients%20like%20coriander.%20That%20dedication%20and%20care%20is%20what%20we%20have%20inherited%20from%20her.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%20dir%3D%