s%2C%20grains%2C%20and%20spices%20including%20lemons%2C%20moringa%2C%20Caprica%20chilies%2C%20pomegranate%2C%20sugarcane%2C%20turmeric%2C%20wheat%2C%20paddy%2C%20guavas%2C%20cauliflower%2C%20spinach%2C%20onions%2C%20beetroot%2C%20ginger%2C%20carrot%2C%20and%20more%20through%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F197256%2Ftelangana-couple-zero-budget-natural-farming-organic-mango-navara-rice-india%2F%23google_vignette%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ezero%20budget%20natural%20farming%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EZero%20input%20cost%2C%20double%20income%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20Jaswinder%20and%20Ranjit%2C%20using%20chemicals%20to%20boost%20production%20from%20the%20field%20was%20the%20only%20way%20to%20farm.%20But%20the%20soil%20kept%20asking%20for%20more.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20noticed%20that%20our%20fertiliser%20usage%20kept%20increasing%20every%20year.%20Initially%2C%20we%20were%20able%20to%20grow%20our%20produce%20using%205-7%20kg%20of%20urea%2C%20however%2C%20we%20were%20later%20forced%20to%20add%2010-12%20kg%20per%20%3Cem%3Ebigha%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAlso%2C%20there%20were%20additional%20input%20costs%20for%20recurring%20fertiliser%20and%20pesticide%20usage.%20The%20input%20costs%20for%20us%20were%20Rs%202%2C000%20per%20%3Cem%3Ebigha%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%20a%20season.%20Now%2C%20this%20has%20been%20reduced%20to%20zero%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20name%20suggests%2C%20there%20are%20zero%20production%20costs%20in%20zero-budget%20natural%20farming.%20It%20is%20the%20practice%20of%20growing%20crops%20that%20eliminates%20the%20application%20of%20chemical%20inputs%20like%20urea.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20are%20a%20lot%20of%20advantages%20of%20natural%20farming%2C%20the%20first%20one%20being%20the%20availability%20of%20toxin-free%20food%20and%20rejuvenated%20soil%20health%2C%E2%80%9D%2