3E%E2%80%9CToday%2C%20we%20get%20three%20quintals%20of%20produce%20per%20%3Cem%3Ebigha%3C%2Fem%3E.%20One%20of%20the%20advantages%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F321571%2Famith-kishan-quits-job-to-start-hebbuvu-organic-and-natural-farming-earns-crores%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enatural%20farming%20%3C%2Fa%3Eis%20that%20although%20the%20production%20is%20the%20same%2C%20the%20rate%20of%20this%20produce%20is%20double.%20For%20instance%2C%20our%20wheat%20is%20sold%20at%20Rs%204%2C000%20whereas%20the%20inorganic%20wheat%20is%20for%20Rs%202%2C200%20per%20quintal.%20Similarly%2C%20our%20sugar%20is%20priced%20at%20Rs%20100%2C%20compared%20to%20Rs%2050-60%20per%20kg%20from%20the%20market%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20points%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20zero%20cost%20of%20production%2C%20the%20couple%20has%20doubled%20their%20income%20from%20Rs%2055%2C000%20to%20Rs%201.5%20lakh%20by%20selling%20vegetables%20and%20fruits.%20Their%20produce%20has%20earned%20a%20huge%20demand%20among%20the%20local%20schools%2C%20teachers%2C%20and%20officials.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJaswinder%20also%20processes%20the%20low-grade%20vegetables%20into%20pickles%2C%20vinegar%2C%20and%20chutneys.%20Annually%2C%20she%20processes%20up%20to%20eight%20quintals%20of%20vegetables%20like%20lemons%2C%20cauliflower%2C%20reddish%2C%20beetroot%2C%20and%20ginger%20into%20value-added%20products.%20This%20earns%20them%20an%20additional%20income%20of%20Rs%201%20lakh%20annually.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fhimachal-1717133355.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20couple%20cultivates%20at%20least%2025%20kinds%20of%20fruits%2C%20vegetables%2C%20grains%2C%20and%20spices%20through%20natural%20farming.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%